# Cross-origin isolation headers required by the audio worklet (SharedArrayBuffer).
# Format: Netlify / Cloudflare Pages "_headers" file. Deploy this at the site
# root (or the /audiogame folder root). For other hosts, set the same two
# headers via their config (see README):
#   Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
#   Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp

/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
